Package com.example.homeheirs

Class Item

java.lang.Object
com.example.homeheirs.Item
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Item extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an item in the item list. Each item has a name, purchase date, description, make, model, serial number, estimated value, additional comments, and an optional list of tags. Implements Serializable to support serialization, and can be used for data storage or communication between activities.
